{
  "stem": "14737.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there are commanders, and soldiers, and guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like in every day--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And alas, there were several labor camps, not in the same place were we were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were where the Jewish community were, and other places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these units are assigned also all to go to the Soviet occupied territory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We know that everyone who goes to watch later will go to the Soviet occupied territory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is a-- was a commander by the name of [NON-ENGLISH], Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was like, not a colonel, I would say a [NON-ENGLISH]-- an officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was in command of the whole town, a whole this operation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was sending out every week one or two units.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a [NON-ENGLISH], like on a white horse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I'm coming there, doctor, lawyers, accountants, business people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I find myself nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are just in the beginning of labor camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They don't anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there are a sergeant by the name of [NON-ENGLISH] who was in charge of all our unit of our 200 people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A harsh man, a wild man, a drunk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a first World War-- he was, what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A soldier.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he became now, not an officer-- he hardly can speak Hungarian, his own language.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was employed in the city of Budapest as lighting up lamps in the park.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, can imagine, he become-- not the commander, executor of-- and punishment, and going on are all kind, and there are more.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So questions are being asked in roll call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who was this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who was that?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everyone was saying his profession.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it comes to my profession, what am I going to say?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm a wood chopper.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
